OL,5,G0005 24 Hours in A&E
OL,6,     FBrian, who's 74, is taken to
OL,7,     FKing's by ambulance after falling
OL,8,     Fdown some stairs. His partner
OL,9,     FMargaret discusses their life
OL,10,     Ftogether and the challenges of his
OL,11,     Fsevere dementia.
OL,12,G0105 999: On the Front Line
OL,13,     FParamedics respond to reports of a
OL,14,     Fpatient in cardiac arrest. But
OL,15,     Fwhen they arrive, there's no
OL,16,     Fanswer at the door. A boy has an
OL,17,     Fepileptic seizure during a PE
OL,18,     Flesson.
